Calls.Name: copyButton.addEventListener
Args:
(el) =>
      navigator.clipboard.writeText([
        el
          .composedPath()
          .find((el) => el.classList.contains(buttonClassName))
          .previousElementSibling.textContent.split("\n")
          .map((s) => s.trim())
          .filter(
            (s, ix, arr) =>
              s.startsWith("$") || (ix > 0 && arr[ix - 1].endsWith("\\"))
          )
          .map((s) => s.replace(/^\$\s+/, ""))
          .join("\n"),
      ])
